<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN236-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇai – atu. tuṟai – kaiyaṟunilai. vēḷpārituñciyavaḻi makaḷiraip pārppārppaṭuttu vaṭakkirunta kapilar pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN236">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kalaiyuṇak kiḻinta muḻavumaruḷ perumpaḻañ</l>
<l>cilaikeḻu kuṟavark kalkumicai vāku</l>
<l>malaikeḻu nāṭa māvaṇ pāri</l>
<l>kalanta kēṇmaik kovvāy nīyeṟ</l>
<l>pulantaṉai yākuvai puranta yāṇṭē</l>
<l>peruntaku ciṟappi ṉaṭpiṟ kollā</l>
<l>toruṅkuvaral viṭāa toḻikeṉak kūṟi</l>
<l>yiṉaiyai yātali ṉiṉakku maṟṟiyāṉ</l>
<l>mēyiṉē ṉaṉmai yāṉē yāyiṉu</l>
<l>mimmai pōlak kāṭṭi yummai</l>
<l>yiṭaiyil kāṭci niṉṉō</l>
<l>ṭuṭaṉuṟai vākkuka vuyarnta pālē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="3ab">O man from a mountaineous land, </l>
<l corresp="1">where the drum-like big fruit that was torn open by a monkey to eat </l>
<l corresp="2">becomes lasting food for the bow-bearing hill people, </l>
<l corresp="3cd">  great generous Pāri </l>
<l corresp="4">you, who are unequal to mutual intimacy, </l>
<l corresp="5">are one who has become vexed with me. For the years you protected [me], </l>
<l corresp="6">[this] is not in agreement with a friendship of befitting great excellence. </l>
<l corresp="7">Without letting [me] come together [with you] you said “let him stay behind”, </l>
<l corresp="8">[and] because you are thus, to you I, however, </l>
<l corresp="9">am [still] attached, even though it may be in absence. </l>
<l corresp="10">Showing itself as in this birth, in the next birth [too] </l>
<l corresp="12">let lofty fate cause [me] to stay together </l>
<l corresp="11">with you of unimpeded sight. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
